論"},{"pid":"e80a8f76731be93a8556f8acd9d3e0898014141f","tid":806841,"uid":3482,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70796a32196d3c2a99ce41be855ed11729365b9d","tid":806841,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"90b8850a21eb249dfd3315082526513999cbec11","tid":806841,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"IT 狗經常預到o既問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"老勞係合約條文上就真係幫你唔到既<br />\n因為真係唔係僱傭條例既野<br />\n<br />\n另外因為最終判決係睇個官點判<br />\n同埋當中既野外人未必知 (例如你咁轉左過去有冇令任何人有捐失等等)<br />\n所以其實法律意見都未必可以好中肯咁答到你<br />\n<br />\n再講返前D<br />\n簽合約你係情我願<br />\n大家都同意左件事<br />\n其中有人違反左, 另一方當然有權追討<br />\n<br />\n而家結果出左黎係咁<br />\n樓主你當然可以大大聲屌對家啦 (個官都判左係對方無理) <br />\n但如果對方又拎得出黎一D證明佢係有損失既<br />\n咁個情況可能係對你不利<br />\n<br />\n事實上呢D野都係好CASE BY CASE<br />\n冇得一概而論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"其實，佢淨係出糧比我，我走咗會對有咩損失先，<br />\n退一百步黎講，我只係一個員工，我走咗你有損失關我撚事咩。"},{"pid":"cab3e2b5efefe6e99b307d18114b044a8d21815a","tid":806841,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b7b4b2063795997baa615ad2f68688cd2ea169a","tid":806841,"uid":15994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"910edef72f48c19129616f9fd630add8540eb853","tid":806841,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cc106372f5d3522e3b809ad9b9dc62cb21f626","tid":806841,"uid":15994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf53